  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.0.0-beta01\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-beta01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-beta01</h3>\n<p>May 7, 2019</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.concurrent:concurrent-futures:1.0.0-beta01</code> is released.  The commits included in this version can be found <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/033f65978071d72164b3707a61d342844c9f2811..26b84a56581b60b44efe49f4ee63c95fa8dc8787/concurrent/futures\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>API changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ResolvableFuture</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">AbstractResolvableFuture</code> were hidden from public api in favor <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">CallbackToFutureAdapter</code> that provides safer API.</li>\n</ul>",
